- A query variable is marked by the use of either "?" or "$".
- The"?" or "$" is not part of the variable name.
- In a query, $x and ?x identify the same variable.
- All queries in this wiki use only "?".
- Allowable characters are [a-z], [A-Z], [0-9], _, Â· and diacritics. Hyphens are not allowed.
- When using several words, it is recommended to put them wither in CamelCase or use underscore (Number_Of_Items)